subject: Dog Sledding
Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race (Alaska)
lead_paragraph: The veteran John Baker seized the lead in the Iditarod on the Yukon River and extended it on the 70-mile stretch from Eagle Island to Kaltag, the last checkpoint on the Yukon
